page.title: 09MRS. MACDOUGALL'S DAY. PART1
page.content: 7.30a.m. GOT UP, DRESSED AND MADE BREAKFAST. 8.00a.m. WENT TO TAYNUILT (7miles) TO COLLECT THE NEWSPAPERS, MILK AND BREAD FOR THE SHOP OPENING AT NINE O'CLOCK. 9.30a.m. COLLECTED DINNER CANS AND WENT TO GET HAIR PERMED AT TAYNUILT. 11.30a.m.HAIR PERMED. WENT TO TAYNUILT PRIMARY SCHOOL KITCHENS TO COLLECT MEALS FOR KILCHRENAN PRIMARY SCHOOL. 12.00p.m.ARRIVED AT KILCHRENAN SCHOOL. SERVED MEALS AND WASHED UP. 12.45p.m.RUSHED HOME TO CHANGE FOR SCHOOL PRIZE GIVING. 01.15p.m.ARRIVED BACK AT KILCHRENAN SCHOOL. 02.05p.m.ARRIVED AT SHOP TO OPEN IT(5mins LATE).SERVED GROCERIES AND POST OFFICE.
